{"tid":2353948,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"勞工法例其實係叫僱主必須盡快支付所有工資給僱員，而唔係大條道理拖糧拖到 7 號！","createTime":"2021-01-05T06:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T07:57:16.000Z","uid":280108,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"98f52c9133b20baab8263e8ea073017504f6bcd7","tid":2353948,"uid":280108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"勞工法例講明 <a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/03.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublic%2Fpdf%2Fwcp%2FConciseGuide%2F03.pdf&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuOQhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=af7ad901\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/public/pdf/wcp/ConciseGuide/03.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n支付工資<br />\n工資在工資期最後一天完結時即到期支付，<strong>僱主必須盡快支付所有工資給僱員</strong>，在任何情況下不得遲於工資期屆滿後 7 天。僱主如果未能依時支付工資，須就欠薪支付利息給僱員。 <br />\n<br />\n咁其實係下個月 1 號開始就算係拖糧，如果仆街到 7 號都唔出，咁就係犯法。相信立法原意係想幫一幫  d 周轉唔黎既公司，而唔係大條道理叫 d 公司拖糧拖到 7 號先出人工。"},{"pid":"2f98fc17c527b63a3f72543fcdfb67ad5bd878da","tid":2353948,"uid":5890,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:34:58.000Z","msg":"咁佢7號出無犯法..咁你想佢點"},{"pid":"00b733e23e3ec0924a3ed0892e638e8bdd0a892c","tid":2353948,"uid":8308,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:47:41.000Z","msg":"你就算改到一個星期出一次糧 都一樣大把僱主最後一日最後一個鐘先出"},{"pid":"20fa382779fc721887b98cec3a3fa9b291805f06","tid":2353948,"uid":280108,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T06:55:45.000Z","msg":"拖糧變成合情合理合法，打工仔改變唔到，亦冇呢 d 僱主符。"},{"pid":"cf29fcc5f3d234f1def158293b7721e460c0a634","tid":2353948,"uid":65893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"邊日出糧唔係公司自己定既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />法定每月1號出？"},{"pid":"b5aa3bf1bf72a0208389664ada9cc68c9216a39d","tid":2353948,"uid":165232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T16:30:03.000Z","msg":"我公司月尾出即月糧<img 